{"tid":1170951,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"郵報：C朗代言的一款健身產品被指控虛假宣傳","createTime":"2019-05-25T10:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T15:14:30.000Z","uid":20634,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"516d0535740866811fb13fce466b9b00e4458d65","tid":1170951,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jbgprN2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjbgprN2.png&h=998a8825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日，C朗代言的一款名為SIXPAD的健身產品被指控虛假宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n據廣告顯示，這款產品可以將電流注入佩戴者的肌肉當中，並且可以起到健身的作用。<br />\n<br />\n然而，據專家向《每日郵報》透露的信息稱，這款產品雖然能夠緩解肌肉疲勞，但是並不能起到健身的作用。<br />\n<br />\n這款產品的價格達到了350英鎊。據悉，發售這款產品的公司去年的盈利超過了3.15億英鎊。"},{"pid":"eba971233f13a47500bffda51a25f1b7e6858ba3","tid":1170951,"uid":16256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:56:49.000Z","msg":"350英鎊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc82a4eee5061695201221fad3788138abf1ee9","tid":1170951,"uid":127929,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"入黎諗住係睇康保萊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3VyvnnB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3VyvnnB.jpg&h=b425b5ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37899b2b56677bb5829f5fc8658d96cbef697671","tid":1170951,"uid":53855,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"2bc82a4eee5061695201221fad3788138abf1ee9","tid":1170951,"uid":127929,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"入黎諗住係睇康保萊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3VyvnnB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3VyvnnB.jpg&h=b425b5ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"美斯發育不良原因揭秘  專家指與飲食有關<br />\n- 分享